item.description:
Dock jumping, also known as dock diving, is a dog sport in which dogs compete in jumping for distance, height and speed retrieve from a dock into a body of water.

Hudson Valley DockDogs will be holding a Regional DockDog event on June 9th & 10th in Millerton, NY. They have invited Dog Rescues and Vendors along with Rescue Ink (New York) & the Dutchess County SPCA to join them on this wonderful weekend!

You've never seen an event like this! FREE for spectators! Come support Spark Plug and I (competing on Sunday) at an awesome event in a BEAUTIFUL setting! Event is outdoor in semi-rural NY :)

Email justcassie101@gmail.com with any questions, or check out www.dockdogs.com!
